            >
              CC0 Public Domain
            </a>
          </div>
          <div>
            Meetup icon made from
            <a
              href="https://www.onlinewebfonts.com/icon"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="text-purple-300 hover:text-purple-200 underline"
            >
              svg icons
            </a>
            licensed by
            <a
              href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
